Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Akatsuki"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know and don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get lost! You're keeping me\Nfrom my "art appreciation" time.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:44.57,00:01:48.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヒルコ)あそこか。\N(イタチ)そうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have to take this brat on\Nas my partner?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:48.62,00:01:50.56,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(デイダラ)暁だ？
Dialogue: 0,00:01:50.56,00:01:52.57,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,知るか そんなもん！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, he's full of energy,
Dialogue: 0,00:01:52.57,00:01:55.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オイラのアート鑑賞を\N邪魔するんじゃねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but he seems like\Nthe type to die young.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:55.19,00:02:00.61,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヒルコ)こんなガキを俺の連れに\Nしなきゃなんねえのか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our leader's orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His talent will be very useful.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:00.61,00:02:05.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,威勢はいいが\Nコイツは早死にするタイプだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about my talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who the hell are you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:05.86,00:02:10.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(イタチ)リーダーの命令だ。\Nコイツの能力は役に立つ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We know you're aiding\Nanti-government factions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of neighboring nations with bombings...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:10.58,00:02:13.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オイラの能力を知ってんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Rogue Ninja,\Nbut what is your purpose?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:13.98,00:02:15.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前ら いったい…。
Dialogue: 0,00:02:15.91,00:02:19.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(鬼鮫)近隣諸国で\N反国家分子どもに加担して→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Purpose? I don't need a purpose!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:19.59,00:02:23.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,爆破テロを起こしているのは\Nあなたですね？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I take commissions to\Ncause explosions... using my art.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:23.23,00:02:26.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,抜け忍のあなたが\N何の目的で そんなことを？
Dialogue: 0,00:02:26.65,00:02:29.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(デイダラ)目的？\Nそんなもん ありゃしねえよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he done?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:29.89,00:02:33.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オイラは 依頼を受けて\N爆発を起こすだけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows...?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:33.26,00:02:36.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オイラの作品でな。 うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:36.32,00:02:38.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ウザいな。
Dialogue: 0,00:02:38.59,00:02:41.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(鬼鮫)終わりですか？\Nさあな。
Dialogue: 0,00:02:44.04,00:02:47.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もういい。 俺が やろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me make it clear,\NI won't stop in my pursuit of art!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that you're a part\Nof the Akatsuki,
Dialogue: 0,00:02:57.43,00:03:01.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,言っとくが オイラは\N芸術の追求は やめねえからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you to fulfill your missions.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:01.97,00:03:06.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)好きにしろ。 だが…。
Dialogue: 0,00:03:06.76,00:03:10.02,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,暁に入った以上\N任務には従ってもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.56,Signs,,0,0,0,,BLUE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:10.02,00:03:12.02,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never get caught up\Nin your genjutsu again, hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're one of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that I'll have to\Nuse my genjutsu on you.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:19.77,00:03:22.61,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わかった わかった。\Nだけどな…。
Dialogue: 0,00:03:22.61,00:03:24.67,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そこのお前！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind giving you\Na taste of my art.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:24.67,00:03:27.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,二度と お前の幻術には\Nかかんねえからな！ うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:27.96,00:03:32.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,仲間になった以上 お前に\N幻術をかけることもないだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Partner with Deidara\Nand go kill Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:32.90,00:03:37.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オイラは お前に芸術を\N味わわせてやってもいいんだぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,About time.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:37.47,00:03:41.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それくらいにしておけ。\N(ペイン)サソリ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this Orochimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you on the way.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:41.68,00:03:45.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,デイダラと組んで\N大蛇丸を殺しにいけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru has escaped\Ninto the Land of Wind.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:45.32,00:03:47.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ようやくか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond that, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:47.69,00:03:50.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,誰だよ？ その大蛇丸ってヤツは。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:50.35,00:03:52.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,道々 教えてやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:52.81,00:03:56.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(小南)大蛇丸たちは\N風の国へ逃げ込んだわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You Akatsuki sure like\Nto order guys around...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:56.20,00:03:58.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その先は よくわからない。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:58.68,00:04:02.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それだけわかれば十分だ。 行くぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:03:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi and Kisame,\Ngo to the Hidden Grass Village.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:02.49,00:04:07.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,んっ！\N人使いが荒いな 暁ってのは！
Dialogue: 0,00:04:07.03,00:04:09.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヒルコ)おい 早くしろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What about my partner?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:09.00,00:04:11.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わかったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:11.58,00:04:14.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,イタチと鬼鮫は\N草隠れに行ってもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've ordered Kabuto to keep me\Nupdated through several ways.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:17.00,00:04:19.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(角都)俺の相棒は？
Dialogue: 0,00:04:19.24,00:04:21.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もうしばらく待て。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're headed to\Nthe Land of Wind, this is the spot...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:23.35,00:04:26.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヒルコ)カブトには\Nいくつかのやり方で→
Dialogue: 0,00:04:26.29,00:04:29.56,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺に情報を伝えるように\N命じてある。
Dialogue: 0,00:04:29.56,00:04:34.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,風の国に向かったのなら ここだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Sand Dune of the East...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:40.28,00:04:42.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one place the guys\Nfrom the Village won't go near.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that where you're from, my man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:48.53,00:04:51.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,東の大砂丘…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that location\Nworks out perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:51.24,00:04:55.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なるほど あそこなら\N里のヤツらも そうそう行かねえな。
Dialogue: 0,00:04:55.92,00:04:58.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,旦那のふるさとか？ そこは。
Dialogue: 0,00:04:58.25,00:05:00.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その言い方は やめろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his hideout.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:00.36,00:05:02.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だが あそこなら好都合だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow the whole thing up\Nwith my art, hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even know if\Nhe's there or not.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:09.49,00:05:11.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あれがヤツのアジトだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:05:11.95,00:05:15.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オイラの芸術で\N丸ごと爆発してやるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand Snakes!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:15.39,00:05:18.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今 アイツがいるかどうかも\Nわからねえんだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:18.98,00:05:20.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,んっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They know we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:25.41,00:05:27.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,砂蛇！\N(ヒルコ)無駄だ！
Dialogue: 0,00:05:27.78,00:05:29.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,えっ!?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:29.82,00:05:31.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,すでに気づかれている。
Dialogue: 0,00:05:31.82,00:05:34.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,マジかよ。\N行くぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was expecting Itachi to\Nbe the one who'd come...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the ones the Akatsuki sent?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to kill you\Nwithout hesitation, you traitor.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:41.96,00:05:45.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(大蛇丸)てっきり\Nイタチ君が来るかと思ってたけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, do you really think you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the boy from the Hidden Stone...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:45.45,00:05:48.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あなたたちが\N暁からの追手というわけね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be in\Nthe Demolitions Unit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:48.94,00:05:52.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヒルコ)遠慮なく ぶち殺してやるぜ\N裏切り者野郎。
Dialogue: 0,00:05:52.51,00:05:55.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あら できるかしら？
Dialogue: 0,00:05:55.15,00:05:58.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そちらの坊やは\N岩隠れの爆破部隊にいた子ね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep watch from above and\Nmake sure he doesn't get away.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:58.97,00:06:01.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オイラをガキ扱いすんじゃねえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives, my man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that you want\Nto capture him yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since you have\Nno grudges against him, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:05.67,00:06:09.56,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オメエは アイツが逃げねえように\N空から見張ってろ。
Dialogue: 0,00:06:09.56,00:06:13.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんだよ 旦那！\N自分の手でやりたいってのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want back-up,\Njust call on me at any time, hmm!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:13.04,00:06:17.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ああ。\Nオメエはアイツに恨みはねえだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the geographical\Nadvantage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:20.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,THREE
Dialogue: 0,00:06:20.85,00:06:24.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,援護が欲しくなったら\Nいつでも言ってくれよ。 うん！
Dialogue: 0,00:06:27.40,00:06:30.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ここでは 俺に地の利がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your work, my man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're aware of\Nthe Third Kazekage's power, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My hobby is to collect things\Nthat I find interesting,
Dialogue: 0,00:06:38.02,00:06:40.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あれが 旦那の作品か。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so I took a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:40.17,00:06:44.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,三代目風影の力は\Nテメエも知ってるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:47.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,THREE
Dialogue: 0,00:06:44.85,00:06:49.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ええ 私 いいと思ったものは\N取り入れる主義だから→
Dialogue: 0,00:06:49.74,00:06:51.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,少しいただいたのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that over there?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:01.87,00:07:03.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ん？ なんだと!?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:03.92,00:07:06.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あ？ あっちのは何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Sasori...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard, how dare\Nyou do this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, you damn snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It‘s the Third Kazekage\Nthat you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I used a Forbidden Jutsu\Nto resurrect him.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:16.06,00:07:19.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,サソリか。 キサマよくも この俺を…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Things won't go the way\Nthey did last time...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:19.85,00:07:22.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヒルコ)そいつは何だ？ 蛇野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of your resentful complaints...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:22.06,00:07:25.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(大蛇丸)あなたが殺した\N三代目風影よ。
Dialogue: 0,00:07:25.18,00:07:28.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私が禁術を使って\N蘇らせたの。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:28.90,00:07:31.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今度は 前のようにはいかぬぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,With your Human Puppet...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:31.41,00:07:33.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,恨み節は そこまで。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and my Forbidden Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see which is superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:38.42,00:07:40.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,さて…。
Dialogue: 0,00:07:40.73,00:07:45.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あなたの その人傀儡と\N私の禁術→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Sand: Scattered Showers!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:45.39,00:07:48.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どちらが上かしらね？
Dialogue: 0,00:07:48.29,00:07:50.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,テメエ！
Dialogue: 0,00:07:52.63,00:07:54.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,砂鉄時雨！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the real thing,
Dialogue: 0,00:08:03.46,00:08:05.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うわっ うわ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the puppet stops working when\NIron Sand gets into it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lecture me about puppets!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:12.41,00:08:16.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,傀儡は 砂が中に入ったら\N動きが止まるんでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:16.58,00:08:20.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,テメエが\N傀儡の講釈垂れるんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the real thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've built in lots of hidden tricks\Ninto the puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:36.92,00:08:40.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,傀儡のほうにゃ\N中に いろいろ仕込んでんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one form of immortality...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't die, even though\Nit's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:40.63,00:08:43.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,次は テメエの番だぜ。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:43.27,00:08:45.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way it can't die!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:45.59,00:08:47.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何だ？
Dialogue: 0,00:08:47.64,00:08:50.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これも１つの永遠の命。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:50.43,00:08:53.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死なないのよ 死んでるけど。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:53.32,00:08:56.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死なねえわけがあるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Heargh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?! How do you like my art?!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:13.38,00:09:15.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,喝！
Dialogue: 0,00:09:20.04,00:09:23.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうだ オイラの芸術は！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't it die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After you two die, I'll resurrect you\Nboth in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, what I really wanted...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:33.35,00:09:35.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんで死なねえ？
Dialogue: 0,00:09:35.32,00:09:41.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あなたたちも死んだあと\N同じように蘇らせてあげるわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,was Itachi's body.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:41.20,00:09:45.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もっとも私が\N本当に欲しかったのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My man!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:45.84,00:09:48.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,イタチ君の体なんだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that guy have a weakness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Resurrection isn't one of\Nthe Third's abilities...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:55.21,00:09:58.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,旦那 アイツに弱点ってないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You are both going to become\Nmy pawns forever.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:58.09,00:10:03.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,復活するのは\N三代目の能力じゃないんだ。 クッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop kidding around...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:07.94,00:10:11.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,永遠に私の手駒になるのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I... am the Third Kazekage...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:16.07,00:10:19.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,your pawn!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:19.11,00:10:23.71,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は 三代目風影だぞ。
Dialogue: 0,00:10:25.79,00:10:29.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は… 駒じゃねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if my jutsu wasn't complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:36.55,00:10:41.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おやまぁ\N術が完全でなかったのかしら？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:41.32,00:10:43.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,食らいやがれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:47.94,00:10:50.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やったか。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Heargh!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:53.81,00:10:55.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,逃げんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:10:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Art is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,... an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:01.43,00:11:03.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, c'mon now...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:07.81,00:11:11.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,芸術は 爆発だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We thoroughly searched\Nthe mountain of rubble,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but we didn't find his corpse.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:13.85,00:11:15.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヒルコ)おいおい…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can't say for sure\Nthat we killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's alive,\NI swear I'll kill him myself.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:21.13,00:11:24.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヒルコ)瓦礫の山を\Nくまなく捜したが→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, what was with\Nthat ridiculous jutsu?!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:24.52,00:11:26.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,野郎の死体は見つからなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:26.98,00:11:29.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,殺したとは言い切れねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably the Second Hokage's\NReanimation Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:29.43,00:11:32.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(デイダラ)もし生きてたら\Nぜってぇ オイラの手で殺してやる。
Dialogue: 0,00:11:32.98,00:11:36.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だいたい あのデタラメな術は何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You bring the dead back to life,\Nand control them like a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:36.82,00:11:38.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)何か知っているか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't kill it even if you tried.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:38.95,00:11:41.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(イタチ)おそらく\N二代目火影が開発した→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So you must use a Sealing Jutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or suppress their movement forcefully.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:41.89,00:11:43.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,穢土転生の術だ。
Dialogue: 0,00:11:43.78,00:11:47.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死者を蘇らせ\N自分の意のままに操る。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to kill Orochimaru, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that won't stop a reanimated being...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:47.32,00:11:49.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,殺そうにも殺せない。
Dialogue: 0,00:11:49.47,00:11:51.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だから封印術を使うか→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:51.85,00:11:54.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,力ずくで動きを\N拘束するしかないだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Be wary of Orochimaru from now on.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:54.83,00:11:57.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(デイダラ)大蛇丸を殺せばいいんだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's alive,\Nhe's bound to make another move.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:57.17,00:12:00.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(イタチ)それでも穢土転生体は\N止まらないはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily, no one could\Nsurvive that explosion, hmm.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:00.26,00:12:02.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何だよ そりゃあ。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:02.33,00:12:05.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)今後 大蛇丸に関して\N注意を払え。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No one who joins us is ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:05.52,00:12:08.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,生きていれば\Nなんらかの動きがあるだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Another immortal has appeared\Nout of the woodwork.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:08.65,00:12:10.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(デイダラ)普通 あの爆発で→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a request from\Nthe Land of Steam.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:10.68,00:12:13.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死んでねえはずがないんだがな\Nうん。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A homicidal maniac\Nhas appeared
Dialogue: 0,00:12:13.14,00:12:17.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヒルコ)ここに来るヤツは\N皆 普通じゃねえからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and they want us to eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they have\Ntheir own Hidden Steam shinobi?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:17.20,00:12:20.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(小南)不死身ということでは\Nもう１人 現れたわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, they can't kill it.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:20.87,00:12:22.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)湯の国からの依頼だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So this homicidal maniac\Nis immortal too?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:22.82,00:12:26.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,殺人鬼が現れたので\N退治してほしいそうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he "reani-whatevered"\Nby Orochimaru too?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:26.53,00:12:29.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(角都)あそこにも湯隠れの忍が\Nいるだろうが。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dispatching\Na different team this time.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:29.50,00:12:31.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(小南)彼らでは殺せないそうなの。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:31.86,00:12:34.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(イタチ)その殺人鬼が\N不死身というわけか。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:34.55,00:12:38.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(デイダラ)じゃあ ソイツも大蛇丸の\N穢土なんとか とかか？
Dialogue: 0,00:12:38.59,00:12:42.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)今回は編成をかえて\Nメンバーを派遣する。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to join\Nthe Way of Jashin?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:53.57,00:12:55.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(飛段)そこのアンタ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't for money or revenge.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:58.00,00:13:01.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ジャシン教に入らねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This was out of\Na deep desire to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other ways\Nto quench blood thirst...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He had some other purpose.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:07.93,00:13:10.57,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(角都)金目当てでもなけりゃ\N恨みでもない。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have\Na way of irritating me.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:10.57,00:13:13.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,単に殺したくて殺したな。
Dialogue: 0,00:13:13.11,00:13:16.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,殺戮がしたいのなら\N別のやり方もある。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you... Did you come to\Nmake sure I don't kill Itachi?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:16.79,00:13:19.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何か目的があってのことだろう。
Dialogue: 0,00:13:19.93,00:13:24.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やはり 俺をイラッとさせやがるな\Nテメエは。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no other\NSensory types besides me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The others certainly aren't\Ncut out to be decoys.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:26.62,00:13:29.75,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それで お前は\N俺がイタチを殺さないように→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Decoys?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:29.75,00:13:31.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,見張りに来たのか？
Dialogue: 0,00:13:31.78,00:13:34.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(小南)他に感知タイプがいないから。
Dialogue: 0,00:13:34.25,00:13:39.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それに 他のメンバーでは\Nとてもオトリにはなれないから。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:39.33,00:13:41.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オトリ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to join\Nthe Way of Jashin?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:47.28,00:13:49.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Way of Jashin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the Way of Jashin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can kill people and\Nyou won't be punished.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:53.83,00:13:58.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よう そこのアンタ！\Nジャシン教に入らねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:14:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it just pleases\NLord Jashin even more.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:58.82,00:14:02.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ジャシン教？\Nそうだ ジャシン教だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:02.38,00:14:04.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どういうものなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?\NIsn't that a wonderful teaching?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:04.50,00:14:07.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,人を殺しても\Nなんら裁かれることはない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you interested in joining?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the homicidal maniac...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:07.49,00:14:11.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それどころか ジャシン様は更に\Nお喜びになるんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Homicidal maniac?\NThat's not it at all.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:11.66,00:14:13.67,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そう。
Dialogue: 0,00:14:13.67,00:14:17.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうだ すばらしい教えだろう。\N入る気になったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just offering up prayers\Nto Lord Jashin.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:17.81,00:14:22.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やはり あなたが\N連続殺人鬼というわけね。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll just have to\Noffer you up to Lord Jashin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:22.15,00:14:25.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,殺人鬼？ そりゃねえぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to be\Na Reanimation.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:25.17,00:14:28.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は ジャシン様に\N祈りを捧げてるだけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll test him to see\Nhow immortal he is.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:28.98,00:14:33.02,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前も ジャシン様に\N捧げるしかねえようだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys,\Ndressed up all the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You in an orchestra or\Nband or something?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:33.02,00:14:37.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どう？\N穢土転生ではないようだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... The gloomy one\Nover there plays bass...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:37.00,00:14:40.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なら どういう不死身か\N俺が試してやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl does vocals and keyboards...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:40.52,00:14:44.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんだ お前ら\Nそろいの服着て楽団か？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, maybe that guy there\Ndoes vocals?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:44.49,00:14:49.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,音楽ユニットか？ そこの\Nうっとうしそうなのがベースで→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Lord Jashin would like\Nyou guys as an offering.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:49.55,00:14:52.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんが ボーカル兼キーボード。
Dialogue: 0,00:14:52.23,00:14:55.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いや ボーカルはそっちの兄ちゃんか？
Dialogue: 0,00:14:55.17,00:14:58.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなんじゃねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NIs running around all you can do?!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:58.27,00:15:01.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こりゃあ\Nジャシン様も喜びそうな生贄だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:07.69,00:15:11.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(飛段)ハッハッハッ！\Nどうした 逃げてばっかりか？
Dialogue: 0,00:15:11.38,00:15:13.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,逃がすかよ！
Dialogue: 0,00:15:13.54,00:15:15.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,フッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Done so soon?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:18.76,00:15:20.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,グホッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:26.81,00:15:30.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんだよ もう終わりか。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll punish you in the name of god!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:32.12,00:15:34.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,痛え…。
Dialogue: 0,00:15:37.22,00:15:40.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,痛えじゃねえかよ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:15:40.76,00:15:42.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ほお…。
Dialogue: 0,00:15:42.73,00:15:45.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,神の裁きをくだしてやるぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not gonna help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the rumors about\Nyour immortality are true.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:52.15,00:15:54.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ぐっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:57.07,00:16:00.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう いらねえんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,00:16:00.65,00:16:03.75,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,不死身の噂は本当らしいな。
Dialogue: 0,00:16:03.75,00:16:07.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,さあ 儀式の始まりだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Die...!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:15.13,00:16:18.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,すべての準備は 整った。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,One stab into the heart...
Dialogue: 0,00:16:18.26,00:16:22.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死ね～！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels so good...
Dialogue: 0,00:16:25.70,00:16:27.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:16:27.65,00:16:30.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,心の臓をひと突きだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory be to Lord Jashin!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:32.66,00:16:34.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,テッ テメエ！
Dialogue: 0,00:16:34.93,00:16:39.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,きっ 気持いい。
Dialogue: 0,00:16:39.16,00:16:41.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ジャシン様に栄光を！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard... You got some nerve...
Dialogue: 0,00:16:41.81,00:16:44.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ぐっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... Why didn't you die?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:44.23,00:16:47.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He licked Kakuzu's blood
Dialogue: 0,00:16:52.32,00:16:55.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,テメエ よくも やってくれたな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then mentioned something\Nabout a ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably some jutsu too.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:55.42,00:16:58.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(飛段)おいおい\Nなんで 死なねえんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:17:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He passes on any damage he sustains\Nto the one whose blood he licks.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:58.16,00:17:01.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ぶち殺す。\Nできねえよ。
Dialogue: 0,00:17:01.13,00:17:03.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何か わかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that doesn't\Nexplain his immortality.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:03.17,00:17:06.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヤツは 角都の血を舐め\N儀式と言ったが→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you separate them?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:06.51,00:17:08.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あれも 何らかの術だろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to eliminate him?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:08.87,00:17:13.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自分の受けたダメージを\N血を舐めた相手にも与えるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:13.36,00:17:16.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だが 不死身のわけは わからない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:16.72,00:17:18.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(小南)２人を分けてくれる？
Dialogue: 0,00:17:18.90,00:17:21.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(イタチ)退治するんじゃないのか？\N(小南)ええ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea, Itachi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems they're recruiting him.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:27.54,00:17:29.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なっ なんだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me? I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:33.57,00:17:36.37,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(角都)イタチ 何の真似だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the Akatsuki is...
Dialogue: 0,00:17:36.37,00:17:39.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,仲間に誘うそうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a mission to spread\Nthe Way of Jashin.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:39.53,00:17:43.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あんなヤツをか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should join the Akatsuki\Nfor the sake of your mission too.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:43.22,00:17:47.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(飛段)冗談だろう。 断る。\N暁だか何だか知らねえが→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassinations, war, you name it,
Dialogue: 0,00:17:47.73,00:17:51.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺には ジャシン教の布教という\N使命がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the Akatsuki will do anything...\Nsince we're a band of killers.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:51.22,00:17:54.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(小南)\Nあなたの その使命のためにも→
Dialogue: 0,00:17:54.06,00:17:57.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,暁に入ったほうがいいわ。\Nなんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,00:17:57.95,00:18:03.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,暁は 暗殺 戦争\N何でもやる殺戮集団だから。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to continue propagating\Nthe Way of Jashin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:11.12,Signs,,0,0,0,,THREE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our two-man teams are in place.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:12.24,00:18:16.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ジャシン教の布教は これまでどおり\Nやらせてもらうぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and execute your missions.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:16.07,00:18:18.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,好きにしろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to be\Npartnered with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You took the words out of my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:22.63,00:18:26.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)ツーマンセルも定まった。\Nそれぞれに任務を遂行しろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't irritate me,\Nor I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said. Just try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want your heart.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:29.39,00:18:32.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(角都)\Nまさか お前が俺の相棒とはな。
Dialogue: 0,00:18:32.43,00:18:34.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それは こっちのセリフなんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,00:18:34.89,00:18:37.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺をイラつかせるな。 殺すぞ。
Dialogue: 0,00:18:37.76,00:18:40.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(飛段)\Nだから 殺してみろってんだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:18:40.47,00:18:42.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(角都)お前の心臓は 欲しくない。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Art...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,... is an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's art!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't get what\Nyour art is about.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:59.00,00:19:01.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(デイダラ)芸術は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, you'll understand the aesthetics\Nof something that's fleeting, hmm.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:03.75,00:19:06.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,爆発だ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:19:06.63,00:19:08.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うん？ アートだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? It's the leader.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:08.94,00:19:12.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オメエの芸術は\Nいまいち わかんねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A shinobi village named\Nthe Hidden Sound
Dialogue: 0,00:19:12.81,00:19:15.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(デイダラ)一瞬にして\N儚く散る美学ってのに→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,recently came into existence.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:15.47,00:19:18.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,旦那も\Nそろそろ 目覚めるんだな。 うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that\NOrochimaru is involved.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:18.44,00:19:21.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヒルコ)ん… リーダーだ。\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:21.28,00:19:26.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)音隠れという忍の里が\N最近 誕生した。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you two to\Ncovertly check them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you guys specialize in sneaking\Naround behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:26.46,00:19:32.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この里の成り立ちに 大蛇丸が\N関わっている可能性がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And make him go boom!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:32.27,00:19:34.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あの野郎が！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The orders were to do it covertly.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:34.32,00:19:36.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ペイン : お前たちで\N密かに調査しろ》
Dialogue: 0,00:19:36.44,00:19:41.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ケッ 裏でコソコソやるのが\N得意な野郎だからな。
Dialogue: 0,00:19:41.50,00:19:45.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いっちょ見せつけてやるか\Nドカンとな！
Dialogue: 0,00:19:45.16,00:19:48.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,密かにと言われたろうが。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's been an incident{\i0}\N{\i1}at the Hidden Leaf Village.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Orochimaru's behind it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Orochimaru used shinobi from{\i0}\N{\i1}the Hidden Sound and Hidden Sand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to wage war against the Leaf...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:20:04.92,00:20:08.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ペイン : 木ノ葉隠れの里で\N事件が起きた。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he failed to completely{\i0}\N{\i1}destroy the Leaf.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:20:08.31,00:20:11.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸の仕業だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves him right!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:11.36,00:20:16.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸は\N音隠れと砂隠れの忍を使い→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Third Hokage{\i0}\N{\i1}was killed in battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Orochimaru withdrew,{\i0}\N{\i1}but his whereabouts are unknown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:20:16.04,00:20:20.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉に 戦争を仕掛けたが\N木ノ葉崩しには 失敗したようだ》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll send someone out{\i0}\N{\i1}to investigate, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:20.93,00:20:22.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヘッ ざまあねえや。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll leave this to you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:20:22.87,00:20:26.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ペイン : この戦争で\N三代目火影が死んだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as well as the status{\i0}\N{\i1}of the Leaf's Jinchuriki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:20:26.36,00:20:29.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,引いた大蛇丸だが\N行方は わからない。
Dialogue: 0,00:20:29.38,00:20:31.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,誰かに調査に行ってもらうが…》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they\Naverted total destruction,
Dialogue: 0,00:20:31.55,00:20:33.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺が行こう。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but they've sustained\Nmassive damage.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:33.59,00:20:38.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ペイン : では お前たちに任せる。\N木ノ葉の人柱力の件もな》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That Village was at\Nthe height of prosperity...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That was out of character.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:40.67,00:20:44.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(鬼鮫)とりあえず\N壊滅は免れたものの→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So even you have feelings\Nfor your birthplace, after all?
Dialogue: 0,00:20:44.10,00:20:46.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,被害は 甚大のようですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:46.90,00:20:51.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,栄華を極めたあの里が…\N哀れだな。
Dialogue: 0,00:20:51.29,00:20:53.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,柄にもない。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:53.73,00:20:57.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,故郷は やはり\N未練がありますか？ あなたでも。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke... Are you safe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:20:57.72,00:20:59.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いいや。
Dialogue: 0,00:21:04.45,00:21:06.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まるでないよ。
